\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 Speculative Execution:
\f1\b0 \cf2 \cb3  When given partial specifications, GPT-5 fills in gaps rather than asking for clarification. A request for "a brief on market trends" becomes a 500-word analysis of SaaS market dynamics with specific data points and recommendations.\cb1 \

\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 Tool Proactivity:
\f1\b0 \cf2 \cb3  The model reaches for web search, Python, and Canvas based on implied need rather than explicit instruction. Mention "recent" or "latest" and it will browse. Ask for analysis and it may fire up Python. Request a document and Canvas appears.\cb1 \

\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 Commitment to Direction:
\f1\b0 \cf2 \cb3  After one clarifying question, GPT-5 commits to a path and executes fully. It won't pause mid-way to check if it's on the right track.\cb1 \
