\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 Sensitive Actions:
\f1\b0 \cf2 \cb3  Tool usage can surprise users. A question about "current market conditions" triggers web browsing that may not be desired in certain contexts.\cb1 \

\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 Hidden Assumptions:
\f1\b0 \cf2 \cb3  The model makes silent decisions about audience, timeline, geographic scope, and technical complexity. These assumptions may misalign with actual needs.\cb1 \

\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 Overcomplicated Deliverables:
