\f1\b0 \cf2 \cb3  "Success criteria: (1) actionable recommendations with specific next steps, (2) risk assessment with mitigation strategies, (3) resource requirements and timeline estimates."\cb1 \

\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 Why It Works:
\f1\b0 \cf2 \cb3  Improves first-turn completion rates by giving the model a clear target. Reduces back-and-forth refinement cycles.\cb1 \

\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 Quality Gate:
\f1\b0 \cf2 \cb3  Include what constitutes failure: "Reject if: vague recommendations, missing cost considerations, or no implementation timeline."\cb1 \
